08938c5e3d2b","event_uuid":"a321ae36-dae9-4742-b867-62460245ec6e","position":{"commit_sha":"5586be0a77ad8a93c981ec1873abb9e1581aa0b5","position":"1784776904720032001-a321ae36-dae9-4742-b867-62460245ec6e"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-217_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"b3ee85f1-444b-4969-9577-fe7b5a242d7d","comments":[],"created_at":1784759182972123001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[{"link_uuid":"b5c973d2-283b-43ea-807f-94610db8bc84","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"6673-7636-a116-4f90"}],"description":"## Context\nSplit from S4 (rebar:6673). The reconciler's backend-neutral core still reached the Jira vendor field MAPPER directly after the epic landed: outbound_differ + apply_inbound + reconcile_check import adapters/jira/outbound_fields; inbound_differ imports inbound_fields; and outbound_links held the Jira link map. This routes the core MAPPER access through the Backend port via dependency injection (ADR 0035 §(d)).\n\n## Delivered (mapper entrypoint injected via the port)\n- outbound_differ.compute_outbound_mutations: injected outbound_mapper (Backend-port OutboundMapper), calls map_local_to_remote(); module-level _map_local_to_jira_fields import dropped.\n- inbound_differ.compute_inbound_mutations: injected inbound_mapper, calls map_remote_to_local(); direct _map_jira_to_local_fields import dropped.\n- apply_inbound._build_hard_delete_recreate: resolves the mapper lazily via select_backend(load_config()).outbound.\n- run_differs: production injection point — obtains the configured Backend once and threads backend.outbound / backend.inbound into both differ phases. Injected params default to None, resolving via the neutral select_backend seam (direct differ-test call sites behave identically).\n- outbound_links._RELATION_TO_JIRA_LINK relocated into adapters/jira/jira_fields.py.\n\n## Scope boundary (documented residual)\nOnly the vendor MAPPER entrypoint is routed through the port. Non-mapping helpers with NO port equivalent stay directly imported by the differ (outbound_fields' _diff_fields/_extract_jira_field/_assignee_matches and inbound value maps), and reconcile_check keeps its lazy internal-helper _load_sibling. These operate on the vendor-shaped snapshot and have no Backend-port method; fully relocating them (or extending the port) is a smaller separate follow-up. The neutrality gate documents this boundary explicitly.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] outbound_differ.py, inbound_differ.py, apply_inbound.py have NO module-level import of the vendor MAPPER entrypoint (_map_local_to_jira_fields / _map_jira_to_local_fields); they receive it via Backend-port injection — verified by the AST assertions in tests/unit/rebar_reconciler/test_backend_neutrality.py.\n- [ ] The injected mapper is actually USED by each differ (not bypassed) — verified by positive injection tests in the neutrality gate (a passed-in fake mapper is exercised).\n- [ ] outbound_links._RELATION_TO_JIRA_LINK is single-sourced in adapters/jira/ (jira_fields.py) and imported from there.\n- [ ] Behaviour-preserving: full reconcile unit+integration suite green; whole test tree still collects cleanly.\n- [ ] make lint && make typecheck && make test green.\n- [Documented residual, not this ticket] Relocating the non-mapping outbound_fields helpers + reconcile_check's lazy load off the core (or onto the port) is a smaller follow-up.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/outbound_differ.py","reason":"Receive outbound mapper via injection instead of importing _map_local_to_jira_fields"},{"path":"src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/inbound_differ.py","reason":"Receive inbound mapper via injection"},{"path":"src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/apply_inbound.py","reason":"Receive outbound mapper via injection"},{"path":"src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/outbound_comments.py","reason":"Receive adf/comment sanitizer via injection"},{"path":"src/rebar/_engine/rebar_reconciler/outbound_links.py","reason":"Relocate _RELATION_TO_JIRA_LINK to adapters/jira single-source"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[["parent","bbf1-82e1-cf9d-494a"]],"parent_id":"bbf1-82e1-cf9d-494a","parent_status_uuid":"a7603497-b0bc-4290-aab6-a2c7f7b15cea","plan_review_phase":"execution","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"4af8-2d88-719e-4478","ticket_type":"task","title":"Route reconciler differ/apply core-importer sites off vendor mappers via dependency injection (S4 follow-up)","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["362eadea-3730-4f62-8cb1-d31517c28ca2","b5c973d2-283b-43ea-807f-94610db8bc84","639a268c-f87e-43af-a553-4ab33d5d7038","10a1fa71-d1b4-4478-9b02-4dfb541faf43","a7603497-b0bc-4290-aab6-a2c7f7b15cea","4f41e16b-340f-4ea6-8eae-4b702b99bc47","1f010d67-faa9-4fe1-a81f-849af52abdce","a321ae36-dae9-4742-b867-62460245ec6e"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784776904720032002,"uuid":"af0479e4-b24c-4df8-bbc0-450f9c493616"}